## المرحلة 2 — UserService (إعادة كتابة كاملة) 🔴

### الهدف
استبدال `_unitOfWork.Users/Roles/UserRoles` بـ `UserManager` و`RoleManager`.

---

### [MODIFY] [IUserService.cs](file:///c:/Users/Masoud/source/repos/BloodConnectAPI/BloodConnectAPI.Services/Interfaces/IUserService.cs)

**بعد:**
```csharp
public interface IUserService
{
    // CRUD
    Task<ServiceResponse<ApplicationUserDto>> GetByIdAsync(string id);
    Task<ServiceResponse<PagedResult<ApplicationUserDto>>> GetAllAsync(PaginationParams pagination);
    Task<ServiceResponse<ApplicationUserDto>> UpdateAsync(string id, UpdateApplicationUserDto dto);
    Task<ServiceResponse<bool>> DeleteAsync(string id);
    Task<ServiceResponse<bool>> ToggleActiveAsync(string id);

    // Roles (Identity)
    Task<ServiceResponse<IEnumerable<string>>> GetUserRolesAsync(string userId);
    Task<ServiceResponse<bool>> AssignRoleAsync(string userId, string roleName);
    Task<ServiceResponse<bool>> RemoveRoleAsync(string userId, string roleName);

    // Donor Link
    Task<ServiceResponse<ApplicationUserDto>> GetWithDonorAsync(string userId);
}
```

**التغييرات:**
- كل `int id` → `string id` (GUID)
- `UserDto` → `ApplicationUserDto`
- `CreateUserDto`/`UpdateUserDto` → `UpdateApplicationUserDto` (إنشاء عبر AuthService فقط)
- `AssignRoleAsync(int, int)` → `AssignRoleAsync(string, string roleName)`
- حُذف `CreateAsync` (مسؤولية AuthService)
- حُذف `GetWithRolesAsync` (مدمج في `GetByIdAsync`)

---

### [MODIFY] [UserService.cs](file:///c:/Users/Masoud/source/repos/BloodConnectAPI/BloodConnectAPI.Services/Implementations/UserService.cs)

**إعادة كتابة كاملة.**

**Constructor:**
```csharp
private readonly UserManager<ApplicationUser> _userManager;
private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;  // لجلب Donor المرتبط
private readonly IMapper _mapper;
```

**`GetByIdAsync(string id)`:**
1. `_userManager.FindByIdAsync(id)`
2. `_userManager.GetRolesAsync(user)` → تعبئة `ApplicationUserDto.Roles`
3. جلب `Donor` المرتبط إن وجد من `_unitOfWork.Donors`

**`GetAllAsync(PaginationParams pagination)`:**
- `_userManager.Users.AsQueryable()` مع فلترة وصفحية يدوية (أو `ToListAsync` ثم Page)

**`UpdateAsync(string id, UpdateApplicationUserDto dto)`:**
1. `_userManager.FindByIdAsync(id)`
2. تحديث `FullName`, `PhoneNumber`, `IsActive`
3. `_userManager.UpdateAsync(user)`

**`DeleteAsync(string id)`:**
- `_userManager.FindByIdAsync` → `_userManager.DeleteAsync`

**`ToggleActiveAsync(string id)`:**
- `user.IsActive = !user.IsActive` → `_userManager.UpdateAsync`

**`AssignRoleAsync(string userId, string roleName)`:**
1. `_userManager.FindByIdAsync`
2. تحقق أن الدور موجود: `_roleManager.RoleExistsAsync(roleName)`
3. `_userManager.AddToRoleAsync(user, roleName)`

**`RemoveRoleAsync(string userId, string roleName)`:**
- `_userManager.RemoveFromRoleAsync(user, roleName)`

**`GetWithDonorAsync(string userId)`:**
- `_unitOfWork.Donors.FirstOrDefaultAsync(d => d.UserId == userId)` لجلب بيانات المتبرع

